Ole,

It&#39;s great that the pattern works for you.  I like things that work.  
The only observation I&#39;d make is that when language features lead you to 
adopt a pervasive pattern, one that touches every class, it&#39;s time to 
ask why those language features are getting in the way, and what can be 
done.

